  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Various methods of FDG-PET signal segmentation will be validated by correlation of
      histopathologically measured tumor dimensions in lymph node dissection specimens of
      head-and-neck cancer patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
